node.text:
The toponymic of Xochicalco means "in the place of the house of flowers", composed of the Nahua words xóchi (tl) flower, cal (li) "house" and co a locative "place of". Xochicalco is an example of the Epiclassic period (700-900 AD) characterized by the emergence of settlements in central Mexico after the decline of Teotihuacan and the power vacuum left by it.
Photo by Ignacio Estrada Yaocelotl

node.text:
The Antarctica is Earth’s most remote and least explored continent. It is buried under as much as three miles of ice in some places, but recent satellite imagery has revealed what appear to be the tops of man-made pyramids scattered throughout the ice-covered landscape. The discovery of several four-sided pyramids has ignited another curiosity as to the mysticism surrounding Antarctica. But how is that possible ?

Some claim that the pyramids could be the work of ancient civilisations or alien civilizations, while others say that they are simply nunataks—protruding peaks of mountains buried beneath the ice, shaped by erosion. However, the distinctly shaped sides of each face are what alternative theories see as evidence of the pyramids being man-made.

In 2016, a striking screenshot from Google Earth showed a set of near perfect pyramids, partially covered by snow. Immediately speculation was rife. An additional dome-shaped structure protruding from beneath the ice has raised further questions and perpetuated the belief of an ancient civilization buried beneath that the Ottomans may have been aware of or contacted.

Ancient Astronaut theorists suggest that an ice-free Antarctica may have been colonized by extraterrestrials in the remote past, until a global catastrophe plunged it into the ice age. Today we know that the continent Antarctic was ice-free until about 34 million years ago, when it became covered with ice.

Perhaps hidden beneath the ice of this frozen continent lies the truth about our extraterrestrial origins. ‘The Pyramid In South Pole’ is found at 26GW22FQ+2C and ‘The Pyramid Peak’ is found at 2VV7PHMM+88 on Google Earth. The slopes of both the pyramids are covered with ice and abundantly buried under the ice. The distance between these two pyramids is 2603 kms.

Scientists have also reported strange magnetic anomalies radiating from beneath the ice, the Nazis allegedly made secret expeditions to the continent in search of a lost civilization and government whistleblowers have come forward with claims of strange sightings. Now the important questions are: How were they created ? How old were they ? #rudraism👽

The Seats of Nemrud...!!!

Mount Nemrut or Nemrud is Officially called as Nemrut Dag, situated in the Southeastern Turkey.. It is 2100 m high mountain with lots of broken or damaged by Christian as well as Islamic extremists in the history of Turkey both during Crusades and later Islamic expansions... 

Mount Nemrut has an history as old as the small tribes started inhabitating the region in and around Turkey... During the First Century BC, the region went under a huge political unrest and a kind of civil war among all the tribes...

After the defeat of Seleucid Empire by the Romans during 190 BC, with the aid of local tribes, the Empire disintegrated into many small states... Out of these, Commagene carved out a empire near Mount Nemrut and started acknowledging all the faiths in the region... 

Antiochus l, successor of Commagene, accommodated the Greek, Iranian myths with his own family and making the huge monuments of the Imperial Family claiming themselves to be representing the Gods on Earth, a concept carried from Egyptian civilization which still had effects in the region... 

Nowdays, only the ruins of once a large monumental wonder lies on the Mount Nemrud with stolen tombs and broken or damaged figures and other related artifacts lying in open... Though its a certified UNESCO site still the site is open haven for anyone and still many stories of hidden treasure are heard in the region...
